cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.RO, cs.SY

This paper deals with multi-object tracking and trajectory prediction, which are topics related to computer vision (cs.CV) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The use of self-attention and relational reasoning also suggests that it could fall under the category of machine learning (cs.LG). Additionally, the paper deals with tracking in the presence of ego-motion and sensor inputs, which could relate to robotics (cs.RO) and control systems (cs.SY).
